# Books folder structure
# 
# Each book should have its own folder:
#
#   books/
#     my-book/
#       manuscript.md    <- Your content (required)
#       cover.png        <- Your cover image (required, supports .jpg/.jpeg/.webp)
#       config.yaml      <- Book metadata (optional)
#
# Usage:
#   python merge.py --book books/my-book
#
# Output will be in output/my-book/
